Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:29.60,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}そっと忍ばす {\fscx75}My heart is a trap and bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:34.90,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}Ah-ah-ah 群がる視線を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:35.94,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx75}Who's the survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.16,Undead OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fscx85}勝負は一度きり
